name: ​​The Bliss of the Same
description:
Much easier in a routine, no surprises.
Every day is exactly the same...

Life in a certain order...
Living in a circle. Ouroboros.
Is this heaven? All in order, away from all the chaos.
Nothing unexpected. I see the bliss of ignorance. I close my eyes. Keep running in my circle of life. Safe.
